data.description: Welcome to Wild Stallions Estates, where luxury living meets breathtaking views! This impeccable 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom Lennar home. The great room is perfect for entertaining, and the chef's kitchen is a culinary haven with top-of-the-line appliances as well as upgraded cabinets with soft close features and dovetailed drawer boxes. The tandem garage provides parking and/or space for a workshop. Escape to the tranquil master suite, complete with a spa-like ensuite bath, where you can unwind and recharge after a long day. Three additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for family and guests, each thoughtfully designed for comfort and relaxation. Outside, Water friendly easy to maintain landscaped backyard is perfect for enjoying family time outside. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today!
